{"tid":2239753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選管會將發表報告： 立法會可修例安排優先投票 ， 境外投票要由政府統籌","createTime":"2020-10-12T07:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T08:20:07.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"626f3834a2a6642c2a97173e2a752c26472b25c1","tid":2239753,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/estcDce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FestcDce.jpg&h=de30bb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【選管會稱無經驗做境外投票 建議規管初選】<br />\n<br />\n據悉，選管會今日將就原訂2020年立法會選舉發表報告，當中觸及境外投票利弊及可行性問題，將建議需要充分討論及確保監察機制，同時選管會稱並無經驗處理境外投票，認為要相關政府部門統籌。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，報告同時會再次重申民主派初選並無法律地位，建議政府考慮管制初選活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1286120625064677/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F366243453719070%2Fposts%2F1286120625064677%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=534eddb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1286120625064677/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"88143b0f22e54b1e229edc3784891485ae2bcd72","tid":2239753,"uid":286897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:51:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c443555177db60e8984d69ab15e05e070373e58f","tid":2239753,"uid":18477,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:53:04.000Z","msg":"冇法律地位又需要管制<br />\n你噏乜鳩"},{"pid":"c049feda0d8f11c031a9ce8b456887b059b266e2","tid":2239753,"uid":12554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"626f3834a2a6642c2a97173e2a752c26472b25c1","tid":2239753,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/estcDce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FestcDce.jpg&h=de30bb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【選管會稱無經驗做境外投票 建議規管初選】<br />\n<br />\n據悉，選管會今日將就原訂2020年立法會選舉發表報告，當中觸及境外投票利弊及可行性問題，將建議需要充分討論及確保監察機制，同時選管會稱並無經驗處理境外投票，認為要相關政府部門統籌。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，報告同時會再次重申民主派初選並無法律地位，建議政府考慮管制初選活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1286120625064677/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F366243453719070%2Fposts%2F1286120625064677%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=534eddb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1286120625064677/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:54:20.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾都無人認同過初選有法律地位<br />\n咁枱面規管嘅理據都唔成立喎"},{"pid":"754f667ecfea116939e4bf794857eb52416b7e1b","tid":2239753,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:54:21.000Z","msg":"選管會反中亂港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c8a76694ac57f4bba9246d51f596cb6a40100f","tid":2239753,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:54:23.000Z","msg":"//報告同時會再次重申民主派初選並無法律地位//<br />\n其實有無諗過初選根本唔需要有法律地位<br />\nCom班人出嚟選舉我都唔明有啲咩野咁特別需要被針對"},{"pid":"e6425262211fd4719cd37017cf39302652a9fcd8","tid":2239753,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"仲選條毛咩, 直接委任整色整水, 議會戰線一早玩撚完"},{"pid":"263300a301911977aae6f310cc1e20b774c48d26","tid":2239753,"uid":128417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"境外洗撚監察機制<br />\n條數都係政府講啫"},{"pid":"b495597e85b8701be86878918bcc8d0ef42036df","tid":2239753,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:00:08.000Z","msg":"唔驚 我地有泛民幫我地頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n議會抗爭 盡做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" clas